     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P1SHN1  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN2  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN3  2
     C                     PARM           P1ZANM 15
     C                     PARM           P1KAZI  52
