     C                     ADD  1         W@P4YY
     C                     Z-ADD1         W@P4MM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  1         W@P4MM
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     Z-ADDW@P4YM    D1YMN4
      * N+5
